                >
                    <div class="relative lg:row-span-2">
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-px rounded-lg bg-white lg:rounded-l-[2rem]"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="relative flex h-full flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[calc(var(--radius-lg)+1px)] lg:rounded-l-[calc(2rem+1px)]"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="px-8 pt-8 pb-3 sm:px-10 sm:pt-10 sm:pb-0"
                            >
                                <p
                                    class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-600 max-lg:text-center"
                                >
                                    <strong
                                        >"I am beyond thrilled with my
                                        new website</strong
                                    >, thanks to the incredible work
                                    of Irina Kramer. I wanted
                                    something that truly reflected my
                                    work as a fine art painter, and
                                    Irina made it happen seamlessly.
                                </p>
                                <p
                                    class="my-2 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-600 max-lg:text-center"
                                >
                                    What impressed me most was how
                                    much research she did on her own.
                                    She explored artist websites,
                                    picked out the best elements, and
                                    came back with a fully developed
                                    vision. From adding a short video
                                    of me painting on the "About page"
                                    to designing a layout that
                                    beautifully showcases my work, to
                                    adding purchase options or
                                    registering for a class, she
                                    thought of everything. All I had
                                    to do was provide access to my
                                    images — she handled the rest. The
                                    result is a stunning, professional
                                    site that feels like an extension
                                    of my art. I can’t recommend Irina
                                    highly enough!"
                                </p>
