                            <div class="px-8 pt-8 sm:px-10 sm:pt-10">
                                <p
                                    class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-600 max-lg:text-center"
                                >
                                    "Irina has a strong knowledge of
                                    modern web development
                                    technologies, including
                                    JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and other
                                    related tools. Moreover, Irina has
                                    an eye for detail and always
                                    ensures that her code is clean,
