                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="relative flex h-full flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[calc(var(--radius-lg)+1px)] max-lg:rounded-b-[calc(2rem+1px)] lg:rounded-r-[calc(2rem+1px)]"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="px-8 pt-8 pb-3 sm:px-10 sm:pt-10 sm:pb-0"
                            >
                                <p
                                    class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-600 max-lg:text-center"
                                >
                                    "Irina is passionate professional
                                    always seeking to do the best work
                                    possible, her experience, way of
                                    thinking, patience and skills make
                                    her a very talented software
                                    engineer. I always feel like she
                                    is in control and has a very well
